<i>noun</i>: 포악 [포ː악], 패악 [패ː악], 악성 [악썽], 악랄 [앙날], 악독 [악똑], 극악 [그각] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>포악 [포ː악]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelty; viciousness</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 행동이 사납고 악함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's personality or behavior being fierce and evil.</dd><br>
<dt>패악 [패ː악]</dt><br>
<dd>wickedness; viciousness</dd><br>
<dd>사람으로서 마땅히 해야 할 도리에 어긋나고 성질이 악함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's tendency to do things against the morality that a person should have; and one's personality being bad.</dd><br>
<dt>악성 [악썽]</dt><br>
<dd>1. viciousness</dd><br>
<dd>악한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A bad quality.</dd><br>
<dd>2. malignancy</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 병이 고치기 어렵거나 생명을 위협할 정도로 심함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a disease becoming so severe that it is difficult to cure or it threatens one's life.</dd><br>
<dt>악랄 [앙날]</dt><br>
<dd>viciousness; cruelty</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 악하고 잔인함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's nature being evil and merciless.</dd><br>
<dt>악독 [악똑]</dt><br>
<dd>viciousness; perversity; harshness</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 고약하고 독함.</dd><br>
<dd>A foul, vicious disposition.</dd><br>
<dt>극악 [그각]</dt><br>
<dd>atrocity; viciousness; flagrant cruelty</dd><br>
<dd>더할 나위 없이 악하고 독함.</dd><br>
<dd>Being incomparably evil and spiteful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>